y/plugin-http of module http. Error: Cannot find module '@opentelemetry/plugin-http'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection refused when calling paymentservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to charge card: could not charge the card: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.55.4:50051: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\n基于收集到的监控指标数据，我对系统在异常时间段 2025-06-08T14:10:55Z 到 2025-06-08T14:29:55Z 期间的故障进行分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"pod_processes\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod进程异常重启导致服务性能下降，表现为pod_processes从1.0变为2.0，同时rrt_max和rrt显著上升\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes: 正常中位数1.0 → 故障中位数1.0，但P99从1.0变为2.0；rrt_max: 1788.0 → 2413.0 (+29.75%)；rrt: 1532.62 → 1796.25 (+15.84%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存资源紧张，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes大幅下降导致服务性能受影响\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 8580739072.0 → 6373826560.0 (-29.51%)，P99变化率46.3%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务错误率异常升高，error_ratio和client_error_ratio的P99值从0.0升至9.64\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio P99: 0.0 → 9.64；client_error_ratio P99: 0.0 → 9.64，变化率均为200%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"响应时间显著增加，rrt_max和rrt出现明显性能下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 5123.0 → 8418.0 (+48.67%)；rrt: 933.22 → 1112.36 (+17.51%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析要点总结：\n\n1. **关键异常信号**：`paymentservice-0` 的 `pod_processes` 变化表明可能发生了Pod重启，这是高优先级的故障信号。\n\n2. **资源瓶颈**：`aiops-k8s-03` 节点内存可用量大幅下降29.51%，可